            <p class="mb-30">
              Al-Fakih Trust is here to help. We're an organization that believes
              in lending a hand to those who need it most. Our goal is to make
              life a little easier for people who are struggling, following the
              teachings of Islam about kindness and caring for others.
            </p>
            <ul class="check-style-one mb-40">
              <li>
                <i class="far fa-check"></i>All Noor Trust boasts an experienced
              </li>
              <li>
