                Ramzan food packs, Our specially curated packages not only
                provide essential nourishment during the holy month but also
                symbolize solidarity and support for those in need. Each pack is
                carefully designed to include nutritious staples, ensuring that
                families facing food insecurity can observe Ramzan with dignity
                and sustenance, fostering a sense of community and compassion."
              </p>
              <div class="single-features-item mb-30 wow fadeInDown">
                <div class="icon">
                  <i class="flaticon-pruning-shears"></i>
                  <span class="shape-circle"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
