      <div class="row justify-content-center pb-200">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <!--====== About Image Item ======-->
          <div class="about-img-item mb-30 wow fadeInUp">
            <img src="/assets/images/about/about-3.jpg" style="max-width:370px;" alt="About Image" />
            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: black;">Food Security Initiatives</h5>
            <p class="mt-2 text-center">
              At Al-Fakih Trust, we recognize the importance of addressing food
              insecurity within our communities. Through our dedicated food
              security initiatives, we have been able to provide essential
              support to families facing hunger. Our Ramzan food pack
              distributions, for example, have ensured that vulnerable
              individuals and families have access to nutritious meals during
              the holy month. Additionally, our ongoing food projects aim to
              tackle food insecurity at its root, implementing sustainable
              solutions to ensure long-term food security for those in need.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <!--====== About Image Item ======-->
          <div class="about-img-item mb-30 wow fadeInDown">
            <img src="/assets/images/about/about-4.jpg" style="max-width:370px;" alt="About Image" />
            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: black;">Education Empowerment Programs</h5>
            <p class="mt-2 text-center">
              Education is a fundamental human right and a powerful tool for
              empowerment. Through our education empowerment programs, we have
              worked tirelessly to ensure that every child has access to quality
              education, regardless of their socio-economic background. From
              distributing free books and school supplies to providing
              scholarships and supporting Islamic schools and madrasas, we are
              committed to breaking down barriers to education and empowering
              future generations to reach their full potential.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
          <!--====== About Image Item ======-->
          <div class="about-img-item mb-30 wow fadeInUp">
            <img src="/assets/images/about/about-5.jpg" style="max-width:370px;" alt="About Image" />
            <h5 class="text-center" style="color: black;">Community Development Projects</h5>
            <p class="mt-2 text-center">
              At Al-Fakih Trust, we believe in the importance of holistic
              community development. Our community development projects focus on
              building sustainable infrastructure and empowering communities to
              become self-reliant. Whether it's through the construction of
              mosques, shelters for the homeless, or initiatives promoting
              sustainable livelihoods, we are dedicated to enhancing the
              well-being and resilience of communities. By fostering a sense of
              ownership and pride, we empower communities to thrive and create
              lasting positive change from within.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

