  <h4 class="text-center display-4" style="color: black;">FAQ</h4>
  <section class="faq-section pt-95">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="accordion" id="accordionOne">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="faq-content-box wow fadeInLeft">
              <div class="accordion-card mb-15">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h6
                    class="accordion-title"
                    data-toggle="collapse"
                    data-target="#collapse0"
                    aria-expanded="true" style="color: black;"
                  >
                    What does Al-Fakih Trust do?
                  </h6>
                </div>
                <div
                  id="collapse0"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                  data-parent="#accordionOne"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <p>
                      Al-Fakih Trust is a charitable organization dedicated to
                      providing food aid, education support, community
                      development, and various other humanitarian initiatives to
                      those in need.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-card mb-15">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h6
                    class="accordion-title collapsed"
                    data-toggle="collapse"
                    data-target="#collapse1"
                    aria-expanded="false" style="color: black;"
                  >
                    How can I donate to Al-Fakih Trust?
                  </h6>
                </div>
                <div
                  id="collapse1"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-parent="#accordionOne"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <p>
                      You can donate to Al-Fakih Trust online through our website
                      or by contacting our donation hotline. We also accept
                      donations via bank transfer and check.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-card mb-15">
                <div class="accordion-header">
                  <h6
                    class="accordion-title collapsed"
                    data-toggle="collapse"
                    data-target="#collapse2"
                    aria-expanded="false" style="color: black;"
                  >
                    How does Al-Fakih Trust ensure transparency and
                    accountability?
                  </h6>
                </div>
                <div
                  id="collapse2"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  data-parent="#accordionOne"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    <p>
                      Al-Fakih Trust is committed to transparency and
                      accountability. We regularly publish financial reports,
                      undergo independent audits, and adhere to strict
                      governance standards to ensure that donor funds are used
                      effectively and responsibly.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
